data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in highly desired Crystal Valley Ranch! Newly Built in 2022 and lightly lived in, this home is ready to call your own! Everything is in fantastic condition with new stainless steel appliances, new tankless water heater and as of 1 month ago, a brand new roof! Buyers will love the covered front porch and oversized 3.5 car garage with the tandem workspace for all your workshop and storage needs. Large open kitchen with huge island, white cabinets, granite counters and a walk-in pantry! LVP flooring, LED lighting throughout with new ceiling fans, new central AC, fiber optic wired, radon mitigated, this list goes on and on! Fully fenced back yard with a covered patio and a brand new extended brick paver patio for entertaining and enjoying the beautiful sunny days. Sellers have added extensive landscaping with 4 trees in the backyard, Peach, Lilac, Red Oak and Chinese Oak and 3 more maples and oak in the front yard. Recently added River Rock and french drains, as well. Ranch style living at its finest with a cozy master suite with an oversized walk-in closet. And to top it all off, an oversized lot with a SOUTH facing driveway. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity, book your showings today!
